## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="2d50f-103"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob>不同於<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleBFile>，因為資料會儲存在的伺服器，而不是在作業系統中的實體檔案。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d50f-103">An <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob> differs from an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleBFile> in that the data is stored on the server instead of in a physical file in the operating system.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2d50f-104">它也可以是讀寫物件，不像<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleBFile>，一律為唯讀。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d50f-104">It can also be a read-write object, unlike an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleBFile>, which is always read-only.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2d50f-105"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob>可能是其中一種<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleType>資料型別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d50f-105">An <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob> may be one of these <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleType> data types.</span></span>  
  
|<span data-ttu-id="2d50f-106">OracleType 資料類型</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d50f-106">OracleType data type</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="2d50f-107">描述</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d50f-107">Description</span></span>|  
|--------------------------|-----------------|  
|`Blob`|<span data-ttu-id="2d50f-108">Oracle`BLOB`包含二進位資料，其大小上限為 4 gb 的資料型別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d50f-108">An Oracle `BLOB` data type that contains binary data with a maximum size of 4 gigabytes (GB).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2d50f-109">這會對應至型別 <xref:System.Array> 的 <xref:System.Byte>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d50f-109">This maps to an <xref:System.Array> of type <xref:System.Byte>.</span></span>|  
|`Clob`|<span data-ttu-id="2d50f-110">Oracle`CLOB`包含字元資料，預設的字元為基礎的資料型別設定在伺服器上，大小上限為 4 GB。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d50f-110">An Oracle `CLOB` data type that contains character data, based on the default character set on the server, with a maximum size of 4 GB.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2d50f-111">這對應至 <xref:System.String>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d50f-111">This maps to <xref:System.String>.</span></span>|  
