 <span data-ttu-id="2d50f-121">若要取得<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob>物件，請呼叫<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOracleLob%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d50f-121">To obtain an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob> object, call the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOracleLob%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2d50f-122">您可以建構<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob>這是 NULL，使用下列格式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d50f-122">You can construct an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob> that is NULL using this format:</span></span>  
  
