 <span data-ttu-id="2d50f-123">這項技術主要用來測試是否`LOB`從伺服器傳回是 NULL，如這個範例所示：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d50f-123">This technique is used primarily to test whether a `LOB` returned from the server is NULL, as this example illustrates:</span></span>  
  
